                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.156/256</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-24T11:00:00-05:29">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 24, 1917, 11 a.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The House has passed the Senate bill authorizing the President to come to
                            a settlement with Ports Company.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
